description:
Internal adaptation of a space at lower ground floor with alterations to include:
-Installation of stone tile floor;
-Adjustment and Installation of the existing ventilation system with floor grilles;
-Additional No 4 floor boxes for electrical power distribution within the room;
-New proposed wall mounter electrical socket
-Installation of No 3 electrical wall mounted radiators;
-Removal of the existing plasterboard infill partitions;
